options.content:
# RPM Dependency pipeline

TripleO-CI takes the lastest good build of TripleO and deploys on top of unknown depenencies.

Pending releases for Example:

- CentOS cr repo [link](https://wiki.centos.org/AdditionalResources/Repositories/CR)
- Ansible releases
- Ceph re
- Openvswitch
- Pacemaker

More Details : 
https://docs.openstack.org/tripleo-docs/latest/ci/tripleo_dependencies_pipelines.html

RDO Zuul : 
https://review.rdoproject.org/zuul/status

# How this works

A known good and validated OSP build is executed with specific unkown versions of a particular dependency e.g OpenVSwitch.  
The unknown dependencies are injected into the build.

To find the rpm version difference between the known good build dependency rpm version vs. the dependency being tested refer to the log file for each job.

1. Open the logs link by clicking the job name
2. Navigate to logs/undercloud/home/zuul/
3. View control_test_diff_table.log

  * "Control Package Version": refers to the known good and validated version of the dependency

  * "Test Package Version": refers to the new version of the dependency being tested prior to the packaging teams adding to an OSP build.

```
+------------+---------------------------------+-------------------------+----------------------+
|    Node    |           Package_Name          | Control Package Version | Test Package Version |
+------------+---------------------------------+-------------------------+----------------------+
| repo_query | network-scripts-openvswitch2.11 |     2.11.3-74.el8fdp    |   2.11.3-85.el8fdp   |
| repo_query | network-scripts-openvswitch2.12 |     2.12.0-22.el8fdp    |   2.12.0-23.el8fdp   |

```

# RDOInfo Info

**Purpose:** gerrit checks breaking changes in pinned dependencies.

* [README](https://github.com/redhat-openstack/rdoinfo)
* **project:** [gerrit project]](https://review.rdoproject.org/r/q/project:rdoinfo)

panels.description: Percentage of rdoinfo project jobs that are passing vs failing vs timing out.

targets.query: SELECT count("result_num") FROM "build" WHERE ("passed" = 'True' AND "result" != 'SKIPPED' AND "type" = 'rdo' AND "result" != 'NODE_FAILURE' AND "project" = 'rdoinfo') AND $timeFilter

SELECT count("result_num") FROM "build" WHERE ("passed" = 'False' AND "result" != 'SKIPPED' AND "type" = 'rdo' AND "result" != 'NODE_FAILURE' AND "result" != 'TIMED_OUT' AND "project" = 'rdoinfo') AND $timeFilter

SELECT count("result_num") FROM "build" WHERE ("passed" = 'False' AND "result" != 'SKIPPED' AND "type" = 'rdo' AND "result" != 'NODE_FAILURE' AND "result" = 'TIMED_OUT' AND "project" = 'rdoinfo') AND $timeFilter

panels.title: rdoinfo stats

targets.query: SELECT count("result_num"), mean("duration"), max("duration"),  sum("duration"), sum("result_num")*100/count("result_num") FROM "autogen"."build" WHERE ("type" = 'rdo' AND project = 'rdoinfo') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "job_name"
SELECT "branch", "change", "log_link", "duration", "result", "result_num" FROM "build" WHERE ("project" = 'rdoinfo' and "type"='rdo') AND $timeFilter
